03:25.639 --> 03:27.173
The nationalist government in

03:27.174 --> 03:32.412
South Africa enacted
apartheid laws in 1938.

03:32.413 --> 03:32.846
Who you could marry.

03:32.846 --> 03:33.614
Where you lived.

03:33.615 --> 03:35.815
Where you could walk, be

03:35.816 --> 03:37.484
educated, everything decided by

03:37.485 --> 03:42.088
racist laws backed by police,
army and secret services.

03:42.089 --> 03:43.656
The institutionalized racial

03:43.657 --> 03:45.258
discrimination was designed to

03:45.259 --> 03:46.993
maintain white minority power

03:46.994 --> 03:48.261
and economically suppress the

03:48.262 --> 03:50.330
black and mixed race south

03:50.331 --> 03:56.303
Africans who lived in
townships, mostly in poverty.

03:56.304 --> 03:59.872
In 1923, the African national
congress was formed.

03:59.873 --> 04:02.709
By 1961, it had been radicalized

04:02.710 --> 04:04.176
by the influence of a young

04:04.177 --> 04:06.178
Nelson Mandela, among others,

04:06.179 --> 04:07.880
and formed an armed wing called

04:07.881 --> 04:10.450
the spear of the nation.

04:10.451 --> 04:12.285
Do you see Africans being

04:12.286 --> 04:16.689
able to develop in the country

04:16.690 --> 04:17.690
without being pushed out?

04:17.690 --> 04:20.560
We have made it very clear in

04:20.560 --> 04:24.030
our policy that South Africa is

04:24.031 --> 04:26.032
a country of many races.

04:26.033 --> 04:32.372
There is room for all
the various races.

04:32.373 --> 04:35.908
In 1963, Mandela was charged

04:35.909 --> 04:38.645
with sabotage and conspiracy and

04:38.646 --> 04:41.881
sentenced to life
imprisonment on Robin island.

04:41.882 --> 04:43.350
It would take another 27 years

04:43.351 --> 04:44.917
of silence and injustice before

04:44.918 --> 04:49.088
the inevitable would happen.

04:49.089 --> 04:50.657
Do you believe in apartheid?

04:50.658 --> 04:51.858
I believe according to god's

04:51.859 --> 04:55.495
will that the white race
should be preserved.

04:55.496 --> 04:57.497
South Africa's white minority

04:57.498 --> 04:58.865
under international sanctions,

04:58.866 --> 04:59.866
internal political pressure and

04:59.867 --> 05:03.903
the decline of the communist

05:03.904 --> 05:08.274
threat, Mandela was we
leased from prison in 1990.

05:08.275 --> 05:10.777
In '94, he was elected president

05:10.778 --> 05:15.682
of the new, free South Africa.

05:15.683 --> 05:19.419
♪

05:19.420 --> 05:20.587
